  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Dynamic & Tactical Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a363c55f59f677357128f37f1b2b1c09.poster.avif?t=1772360864\" width=780 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a363c55f59f677357128f37f1b2b1c09.webm?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a363c55f59f677357128f37f1b2b1c09.mp4?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Play as a variety of vehicles</strong>, each with unique <strong>abilities</strong> and shared <strong>general skills</strong>. Master your vehicle’s strengths, coordinate with your units and adapt your tactics to <strong>outsmart threats</strong> in every mission.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Face Relentless Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a04964e4f56a60249b27048ab812260b.poster.avif?t=1772360864\" width=780 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a04964e4f56a60249b27048ab812260b.webm?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a04964e4f56a60249b27048ab812260b.mp4?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Face a different boss in many levels, each with unique abilities and tactics. Plan your strategy and fortify your defenses before they arrive to challenge your outpost. Adapt to their changing attack patterns, exploit their weaknesses and lead your units to victory against overwhelming odds.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Build Your Outpost</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/869dff0c90882b39fbb661eea31eb549.poster.avif?t=1772360864\" width=780 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/869dff0c90882b39fbb661eea31eb549.webm?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/869dff0c90882b39fbb661eea31eb549.mp4?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Build your outpost with <strong>countless options</strong>, experimenting with new gameplay styles and defensive structures in every run. Choose from a wide range of <strong>melee</strong> units, <strong>ranged</strong> units, <strong>heroes</strong>, <strong>support</strong> and <strong>recon</strong> forces; each unlocking specialized <strong>subclasses</strong> as you upgrade their buildings. In the Vehicle Workshop, <strong>every vehicle offers four unique upgrade paths</strong>, giving you endless variations to try and master with each playthrough.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Heroes and Abilities</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/3871e9d584d129ad2a4fd563ef647d39.poster.avif?t=1772360864\" width=780 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/3871e9d584d129ad2a4fd563ef647d39.webm?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/3871e9d584d129ad2a4fd563ef647d39.mp4?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Select your hero and command the battlefield with their unique and various abilities.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Captain Carter</i>:</strong> A tough veteran soldier with a sharp tactical mind.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Spider-Bot</i>:</strong> A fast robot designed for quick hit-and-run tactics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Tankette Kv2</i>:</strong> The Kv2 is a tankette with tough armor that deals area damage.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Dynamic & Tactical Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a363c55f59f677357128f37f1b2b1c09.poster.avif?t=1772360864\" width=780 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a363c55f59f677357128f37f1b2b1c09.webm?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a363c55f59f677357128f37f1b2b1c09.mp4?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Play as a variety of vehicles</strong>, each with unique <strong>abilities</strong> and shared <strong>general skills</strong>. Master your vehicle’s strengths, coordinate with your units and adapt your tactics to <strong>outsmart threats</strong> in every mission.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Face Relentless Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a04964e4f56a60249b27048ab812260b.poster.avif?t=1772360864\" width=780 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a04964e4f56a60249b27048ab812260b.webm?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927780/extras/a04964e4f56a60249b27048ab812260b.mp4?t=1772360864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Face a different boss in many levels, each wi